msgstr ""

#: src/getting_started/leptos_dx.md:205
msgid ""
"If you just want to use the default options from the command line, just run "
"`leptosfmt ./**/*.rs` from the root of your project to format all the rust "
"files using `leptosfmt`."
msgstr ""

