"In this case, it’s helpful to know about the [`Signal`](https://docs.rs/"
"leptos/latest/leptos/reactive/wrappers/read/struct.Signal.html) type. "
"`Signal` is an enumerated type that represents any kind of readable reactive "
"signal, or a plain value. It can be useful when defining APIs for components "
"you’ll want to reuse while passing different sorts of signals."
