"To create your own components with the builder syntax, you can simply use "
"plain functions (see above). To use other components (for example, the built-"
"in `For` or `Show` control-flow components), you can take advantage of the "
"fact that each component is a function of one component props argument, and "
"component props have their own builder."
msgstr ""

#: src/view/builder.md:87
